<i>adverb</i>: 조촐히 [조촐히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>조촐히 [조촐히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cozily</dd><br>
<dd>작지만 아담하고 깨끗이.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being small but petite and clean.</dd><br>
<dd>2. demurely</dd><br>
<dd>행동이나 행실 등이 깔끔하고 얌전히.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being refined and dignified in behavior or deed.</dd><br>
<dd>3. neatly; simply</dd><br>
<dd>외모나 모습 등이 깨끗하고 멋이 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being neat and classy in appearance or looks.</dd><br>
<dd>4. quietly; simply</dd><br>
<dd>조용하고 간단하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being quiet and simple.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>